# Page section copy

- Publish the page title and **section description** via `PageHeader` / `ModulePageHeader` `description` prop.
- `DashboardPageTitle` renders the description **directly under the title** (left column); actions stay on the right.
- Do **not** duplicate the same copy in the page body (`TablePanelHead help`, standalone `<p className="muted">`, etc.).
- `TablePanelHead help` is only for table-specific context that is not the page intro (rare).
- Typography: title `pds-type-title-m-extrabold`, description `pds-type-body-s-regular muted`.
